00:00:17.780 --> 00:00:18.990
İyi misin?!

00:00:19.540 --> 00:00:20.840
Fraxinus nasıl?

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:23.340
Mürettebat üyeleri iyi mi?!

00:00:23.340 --> 00:00:25.780
