00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:55.420
Bir şey mi eksik?

00:03:56.210 --> 00:03:58.710
Günaydın, herkese.

00:03:59.210 --> 00:04:00.500
Suzuhara-san?

00:04:00.500 --> 00:04:01.560
Burada.

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:02.720
Setouchi-san?

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:03.620
Burada.

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:04.720
<i>Bugün gelmedi mi?</i>

