K-Kurumi!

00:21:31.280 --> 00:21:33.930
O-Origami, sen—”

00:21:43.640 --> 00:21:45.610
Ne oluyor?

00:21:47.540 --> 00:21:48.920
Ha?

00:21:50.480 --> 00:21:51.920
Itsuka-kun?

